#

Kefir Pancakes

30 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGlutenEgg

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Description

Fluffy pancakes made with tangy kefir for a delightful breakfast experience.

Ingredients

  • kefir: 1 cup
  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • sugar: 2 tbsp
  • egg: 1
  • milk: 1/4 cup
  • butter: 2 tbsp
  • vanilla extract: 1 tsp
